  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "Spread a layer of olive oil on the bottom of a 9x13-inch cazuela.",
    "Mix crumbled feta cheese with chopped onion and garlic. ",
    "Layer phyllo dough on top of the feta mixture, brushing with olive oil between each layer. ",
    "In a separate bowl, whisk together milk and tabasco sauce. ",
    "Pour the milk mixture over the phyllo dough. ",
    "Season with salt and black pepper. ",
    "Bake for 30 minutes, or until the phyllo crust is golden brown. ",
    "Garnish with chopped parsley and serve warm.",
    "Let the casserole rest for 10 minutes before serving."
  ],
